lyrics:
In the depths of my mind, I started to sway
Lost in the chaos, slowly fading away
Drowning in confusion, searching for a sign
But deep in my heart, I knew I'd be just fine

[Chorus]
I found strength in the darkness, a light within me
Guiding me home through the stormy sea
I lost myself, but now I'm found
In this journey of life, I stand my ground
Style of Music
